p://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=67.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=59.topic"> Next Topic >> </a> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=95%><tr><td bgcolor=#000000><table border=0 width=100% cellpadding=5 cellspacing=1><tr><td valign=top bgcolor=#cc9966 class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Author</font></td><td valign=top bgcolor=#cc9966 class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uaeacuswolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aeacus Wolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wolf</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#993300>(1/15/01 11:58:53 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/heraqofgsmo/aeacus.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A new year begins in the village</span><hr size=1> The large male wolf trots to the entrance of the village.  His large paws sinking just a little into the fresh snow that had fallen this morning.  He stops as looks around. Then sniffs the air.  The village is quiet. He figures the amazons are huddled inside their warm huts.  Aeacus lifts his muzzle and opens his jaws wide, letting out a long howl to those around him.  Letting them know that he has arrived back into the forests of Scynthia. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tiger4157>Tiger4157</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 103<br> <font color=#993300>(1/18/01 9:23:54 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new year begins in the village</span><hr size=1> ::Sartha sits silently in a snow-covered tree on the border of the village, looking out at the land. She wears no cloak, but seems warm despite the cold. Smiles lightly as she hears the wolf's howl and looks down to see Aeacus at the entrance of the village. She nods respectfully to the wolf, then makes her flute appear and quietly begins to play an old celtic song:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uaeacuswolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aeacus Wolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wolf</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#993300>(1/19/01 4:21:53 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/heraqofgsmo/aeacus.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new year begins in the village</span><hr size=1> Aeacus lops into the village, noticing the one amazon noding to him.  As she begins to howl in her strange human way, he cocks his head and perks his ears forward.  He long gate moves him over to the amazon and then sits down a few feet from her.  He continues to listen to the flowing howl, cocking his head back and forth listening.  Then he decides to join her in her strange human howling. He tilts his muzzle to the sky and begins to howl along with the amazons howl.  Yelping yelps dot the music of the wolfs howl, as he joins his amazon sister. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tiger4157>Tiger4157</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 106<br> <font color=#993300>(1/21/01 11:55:46 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new year begins in the village</span><hr size=1> ::grins as she hears the wolf howl along with her song and continues to play. The song was sweet and happy and it rang through the forest and village along with the howl. Sartha could think of no better way to carry on the day than with song. Especially when another joins you:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uaeacuswolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aeacus Wolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wolf</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#993300>(1/23/01 3:33:34 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/heraqofgsmo/aeacus.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new year begins in the village</span><hr size=1> As the human's howl changed to some high notes, this surprised Aeacus.  He was never able to howl as high as this human.  He lifted his hind quarters and put more effort into his howl.  He tried to sing his best and was enjoying the experience.  Soon, in the woods, more wolves joined in the distance.  The whole valley seemed to have joined the amazon and Aeacus in their song for the new year. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tiger4157>Tiger4157</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 117<br> <font color=#993300>(1/23/01 7:23:40 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new year begins in the village</span><hr size=1> ::can't help but laugh for a moment, her song halting for but a second before she regains her composure and joins back in, still smiling. She was surprised at the beautiful harmony the wolves sang to the sound of her flute, and much more the fact that so many had joined the song. But she did not stay surprised for long, remembering that the wolves were more in tune with the planet than humans or gods. They would be celebrating the new year, no doubt. So she continued her song more quietly, her delicate hearing listening carefully to the beautiful song of the wolves:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uaeacuswolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aeacus Wolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wolf</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#993300>(1/26/01 4:17:29 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/heraqofgsmo/aeacus.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new year begins in the village</span><hr size=1> The large wolf turned his ears behind his head.  He could hear someone coming towards the village.  Then he heard the call of the Queen of Scynthia and quickly turned and rushed towards her call. Jumping over obstacles along the way. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tiger4157>Tiger4157</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 123<br> <font color=#993300>(1/27/01 8:38:21 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new year begins in the village</span><hr size=1> ::watches the wolf run off as she ends her song and chuckles::<br>
<br>
&quot;Happy new year.&quot; <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tiger4157>Tiger4157</A> at: 1/27/01 8:39:49 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=67.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=59.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=65.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.threadControl?topicID=65.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=65.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=65.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option value="amazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya">Sisters of Themiscrya<option value="amazonsunitefrm6">Amazons of the Northern Lands<option value="amazonsunitefrm8">A